Package com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.zone

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ZoneCreateCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to create a new Zone.
    ZoneCreateCommand.Builder
    Builder used to build the desired command.
    ZoneCreateResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a ZoneCreateCommand, describing the result of the Zone creation.
    ZoneDeleteCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to delete an existing Zone.
    ZoneDeleteCommand.Builder
    Builder used to build the desired command.
    ZoneDeleteResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a ZoneDeleteCommand, describing the result of the Zone deletion.
    ZoneGetCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to get the details of a Zone.
    ZoneGetCommand.Builder
    Builder used to build the desired command.
    ZoneGetQueryUsageCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to get the details of the query usage of a Zone.
    ZoneGetQueryUsageCommand.Builder
    Builder used to build the desired command.
    ZoneGetQueryUsageResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a ZoneGetQueryUsageCommand, describing the details of query usage of the specified Zone.
    ZoneGetResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a ZoneGetCommand, describing the details of the retrieved Zone.
    ZoneListCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to get a list of searched Zones.
    ZoneListCommand.Builder
    Builder used to build the desired command.
    ZoneListResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a ZoneListCommand, returning the list of retrieved ZoneRecords.
    ZoneQueryUsageRecord
    List record representing a Zone query usage for a particular time period, from the list returned in the ZoneGetQueryUsageResponse.
    ZoneRecord
    List record representing a Zone, from the list returned in the ZoneListResponse.
    ZoneUpdateCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to update an existing Zone.
    ZoneUpdateCommand.Builder
    Builder used to build the desired command.
    ZoneUpdateResourceRecordsCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to update the resource records an existing Zone.
    ZoneUpdateResourceRecordsCommand.Builder
    Builder used to build the desired command.
    ZoneUpdateResourceRecordsResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a ZoneUpdateResourceRecordsCommand, describing the result of the Zone resource records update.
    ZoneUpdateResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a ZoneUpdateCommand, describing the result of the Zone update.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ZoneQueryUsageGranularity
    Search granularity to query the zone query usage records, in the ZoneGetQueryUsageCommand.
